{"tid":437953,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為 Mate 10 賣4780","createTime":"2017-10-16T12:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T05:24:11.000Z","uid":66607,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"070d6bc1fd5ab43f3978436d021c2852c640215f","tid":437953,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"＄4780 買呢部野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實際上，華為 Mate 10 的設計，亦跟傳聞的相差無幾，用上了 5.9 吋 2K 顯示屏，屏幕比例為 16:9，顏色有摩卡金、香檳金、粉紅金以及黑色四種。指紋辨識鍵設於屏幕的下方，而機背則轉用了玻璃材質，具有直向的雙鏡頭設計。同時，Mate 10 的機身厚度只有 8.2mm，並保留 3.5mm 耳機孔。<br />\n<br />\n同場仲有 Mate 10 Pro 以及 Mate 10 Porsche Design，兩部手機同樣具有 6 吋 FHD AMOLED 屏幕，跟 Mate 10 不同的是，Mate 10 Pro 以及 Mate 10 Porsche Design 屏幕比例為 18:9，並會內置 6GB RAM 以及 128GB ROM，但就不支持 microSD 卡擴充。值得留意的是，雖然 Mate 10 Pro 以及 Mate 10 Porsche Design 屏幕比 Mate 10 略大，但機身厚度卻相對更薄，只有 7.9mm。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/209291/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F209291%2F1%2F&d=iHe0AXGv8ycdxYU%2FahLYxywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c27c5fc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/209291/1/</a>"},{"pid":"349145ccfdf24c81d39f2f666d833cf626d1500f","tid":437953,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"其實好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔會買"},{"pid":"a2bcaab490c09aafa7e662550907307c9491ae05","tid":437953,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"同上代同價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce415d81f9be3b28d43089eca5117257603cbac","tid":437953,"uid":15835,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:09:07.000Z","msg"